2001-11-30  Andi Gutmans  <andi@zend.com>

    * zend.c
      zend.h
      zend_API.c
      zend_compile.c
      zend_compile.h
      zend_execute.c
      zend_execute_API.c
      zend_language_parser.y
      zend_opcode.c:
    - Initial support for class constants. There are still a few semantic
    - issues which need to be looked into but basically it seems to work.
    - Example:
    <?php
    	class foo
    	{
    		const hey = "hello";
    	}

    	print foo::hey;
    ?>

    * Zend.m4: - Fix typo

