2001-11-04  Andi Gutmans  <andi@zend.com>

    * zend_compile.c
      zend_compile.h
      zend_execute.c
      zend_language_parser.y:
    - Support instantiation of nested class. The following script now should
    - work:
    -<?php
    -	class foo
    -	{
    -		function bar()
    -		{
    -			print "bar() in class bar\n";
    -		}
    -
    -		class barbara
    -		{
    -			function bar()
    -			{
    -				print "bar() in class foo::barbara\n";
    -			}
    -		}
    -	}
    -
    -	$obj = new foo();
    -	$obj->bar();
    -
    -	$obj = new foo::barbara();
    -	$obj->bar();
    -

